    +portfolio-modal('portfolioModal2', 'kiosk', '../../public/img/kiosk.png', 'kiosk', 'Kiosk 키오스크 Html(Pug), Css(Scss), JavaScript, Jquery, Json 이용하여 구현하였습니다', 'https://github.com/hamjoong/portfolio/tree/main/kiosk', 'https://github.com/hamjoong/portfolio/tree/main/kiosk/build/pdf')

    // 포트폴리오 모달 3
